data.description: Beautifully renovated 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath home on the waterfront! Remodeled kitchen with new granite, backsplash, stove, newer cabinets and appliances! Inviting open layout with new flooring and fireplace!  Other updates include remodeled full bathroom, new water heater, paint, newer windows & sunroom flooring. Oversized 2 car detached garage with heater. Enjoy fishing, boating & relax in the large backyard!
